{"tid":2012857,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點睇「黃色經濟圈」？ 總商會總裁梁兆基：消費者有自由選擇","createTime":"2020-05-12T02:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T06:20:00.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1271dd24af7968bdc68cc6c493d562cdfeaac8b1","tid":2012857,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"4小時前<br />\n<br />\n對於有人推動「黃色經濟圈」，新任香港總商會總裁梁兆基認為，市民有決定消費模式的自由，以暴力破壞則另作別論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/LGh2vWGUBTTK-FUNKoLYhNwEWn8=/1024x576/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/PETJY54GQLOLB2JQHDIIKNFRFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FLGh2vWGUBTTK-FUNKoLYhNwEWn8%3D%2F1024x576%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FPETJY54GQLOLB2JQHDIIKNFRFU.jpg&h=6c9f94e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受中美貿易戰、本地社會事件及武漢肺炎疫情多面夾擊，本港商界正處於水深火熱之困局。新任香港總商會總裁梁兆基接受訪問指出，「香港」要尋求新出路、新定位，整體對香港、商界營商環境仍然樂觀。對於有人推動「黃色經濟圈」，他認為，市民有決定消費模式的自由，以暴力破壞則另作別論。<br />\n梁兆基解構多個影響本港經濟複雜因素，中美貿易戰爭持不休屬新常態，供應鏈遷移卻不代表香港生存空間收窄，商界要研究開拓新市場，探討扮演的新角色，又指國際貿易壁壘更顯香港自由貿易的重要性。<br />\n本港社運未平息，梁指出，社會不安狀況影響商業活動，短期未見改善，明白兩代人持不同意見，處事方法或許有異，故此更要加強溝通，放下分歧，共同讓香港持續繁榮發展，強調「香港的未來屬於年輕人」。<br />\n「商界角色中立，消費者有自由選擇」<br />\n<br />\n中方、政界中人輪流批評「黃色經濟圈」，梁兆基稱商界角色中立，以經營生意來說，最重要是提供物有所值的服務，「消費者嘅選擇係佢嘅自由」，目前難判斷這種消費模式是否長久。然而，用暴力或非法行為破壞營商環境則另作別論，稱商業運作講求公平原則，以暴力打擊不偏好的商舖並非公平做法，又指「有事發生、有衝擊不代表法制基礎出現問題，反而可以畀外來投資者睇到法治運作安穩」，有信心香港可守住法治的基石。<br />\n內外交困再疊加疫情衝擊，梁兆基預計今年經濟將會收縮，料經濟會隨人流、交通限制取消，在低基數效應下出現大幅反彈，惟部份企業倒閉或對經濟造成一定程度損傷，需時兩至三年才能全面復元。在低利率環境下，他料樓市呈穩中偏弱的局面，樓價不會大幅下跌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃珮琳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/finance/20200512/VF4EBS24BAXTGCZ2FJAXLJSTVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200512%2FVF4EBS24BAXTGCZ2FJAXLJSTVI%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HXB8Xc4SSRTU1%2BC3UxNwN9M%3D&h=a5a0dbd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200512%2FVF4EBS24BAXTGCZ2FJAXLJSTVI%2F&h=e2694f3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/finance/20200512/VF4EBS24BAXTGCZ2FJAXLJSTVI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下半文入Link睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab8d8049ff2ed92281fd491aab41311502afaa0","tid":2012857,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:49:21.000Z","msg":"睇下佢幾時俾689屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8cb27b9cdc2901eb07f65e56a94a798c003615","tid":2012857,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"淆底啊？"},{"pid":"10c87660f664b9c0884323e43b1b7b70376623e0","tid":2012857,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:54:25.000Z","msg":"黃暴經濟圈"},{"pid":"98f1e165bbec14d3c6d6867ff37fba84c9664ba5","tid":2012857,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeADPyK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeADPyK.gif&h=675635f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87b46d7be24931b1624657b6b8e32f24011ab3ff","tid":2012857,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"正常商界係食四方飯，所以佢唔屌黃色經濟圈係正常，否則得罪曬黃絲好影響生意"},{"pid":"98727f34f0257cf84b6e814ac3446a0a0a941ebe","tid":2012857,"uid":228396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98f1e165bbec14d3c6d6867ff37fba84c9664ba5","tid":2012857,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeADPyK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeADPyK.gif&h=675635f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.